				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Tone: People trying to act somewhast normal under grave circumstances. Intreactions are intoned with gravity.\r\nThe Bard is inside the kid hideout with the rest of the kids, supposedly keeping an eye on them as they are not to go outside the hideout anymore with the incoming goblin attack. Zaki is trying to act older and not scared and Alfira is playing along with it."
				}
